Notes External seating are of 136sqm (1,465sqft) Rent available on request The Guildhall leisure development provides a unique opportunity on York’s prestigious riverside, set amongst well established food and beverage operators including Jamie’s, Revolution, Carluccio’s and Pitcher and Piano. The contemporary environment created will provide well configured, functional space with the dramatic backdrop of the River Ouse and Lendal Bridge. Operators will also benefit from a roof terrace and riverside garden, as well as an exclusive entrance off Lendal, providing a rare and attractive opportunity in the City Centre of York.
